# Stay Awhile Jam Kit, local environment
#
# The kit needs NO secret keys to run. Authentication is handled by the Rundot
# CLI (`rundot init` / `rundot deploy`), and your game ID lives in
# game.config.prod.json, not here.
#
# This file exists as a placeholder for creators who add their own integrations
# (a custom backend, an analytics key, etc.). Copy to `.env.local` and add vars
# as needed; Vite exposes only those prefixed with VITE_ to client code.
#
# Example:
# VITE_MY_FEATURE_FLAG=true
